{"tid":617481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係我黑心，但條港珠澳大橋出事係對香港好","createTime":"2018-04-05T04:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T09:34:49.000Z","uid":62063,"like":175,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"bae99a686d9ce6e2ba71510f3b7edb1fb275feab","tid":617481,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:07:38.000Z","msg":"前前後後洗咁多錢，換嚟呢啲蔗渣質素<br />\n<br />\n當初要用咁多錢已經引起好大嘅反對聲音<br />\n<br />\n但大家都預期咁嘅經費起碼可以起得正正常常<br />\n<br />\n之後接連出現偷工減料，質素參差嘅消息<br />\n<br />\n大家都知好明顯係俾人貪污貪咗去<br />\n<br />\n而班死弱智仲focus係幾時有得用，遲吓會好方便<br />\n<br />\n完全睇唔到有咩問題㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我諗條橋真係要出事先可以令人反思呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n而家個情況係你被迫夾錢同人哋去酒店食飯<br />\n<br />\n出咗兩個course都係煮到燶晒放唔落口<br />\n<br />\n然後你仲好期待個甜品會好好食，覺得好抵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">瞓醒未啊？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c8a3e856030cb309e7592bee916e48346abc07","tid":617481,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a13de35e597aa35264b956bd9ac891b65a0558","tid":617481,"uid":42229,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:11:27.000Z","msg":"到時又會懶最衰拉布搞到咁<br />\n然後班豬又會信"},{"pid":"1bd276c49de6526be9c244c3417cc7376c02d7d5","tid":617481,"uid":53466,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:11:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e93e896228cc70c88474ab682f8bedbd79bbe061","tid":617481,"uid":175673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"轉頭就唔記得，繼續課水。"},{"pid":"d395b0ba33578892d47863a361d218de574180f1","tid":617481,"uid":31215,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:17:20.000Z","msg":"出呢啲少少事鬼理咩<br />\n香港人：佢地會補救維修架啦，真係用嗰時點會有事<br />\n香港人未出過大災難，唔會有危機意識，唔會唔信政府<br />\n<br />\n要去到成條橋斷左，或者成架高鐵飛出街死一堆人，仲要重複幾鑊，先會動搖香港冇問題嘅想法"},{"pid":"d5e9d0d0a089b650e3021273b008c2240e1eb8d3","tid":617481,"uid":19213,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:20:15.000Z","msg":"咁樣邊叫黑心<br />\n俾港豬繼續生存先黑心呀"},{"pid":"51667a5be0901eeb1493f28bcbd078f00d55609d","tid":617481,"uid":55080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:22:49.000Z","msg":"唔係佔中條橋就唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bf233679345aaa619532983bd7a944a36ac25f","tid":617481,"uid":119610,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:24:44.000Z","msg":"然後haters一定會話係拉布搞到成本上漲，被逼要節省成本而偷工減料，將件事合理化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a1166a9f8927bed161eff242ef0890c05ed2c0","tid":617481,"uid":139816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:27:33.000Z","msg":"邊關事啊 香港人唔係唔醒 <br />\n係醒咗扮訓 冇機會叫醒佢地架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7b9b8e64ae721f1816e76e2bd3d338773bf285","tid":617481,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0e014a0018d91213247e409033c2aa70f05185","tid":617481,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"咁快沉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade403bffc6fbf0a1a21679b533a0aa172efba5b","tid":617481,"uid":140953,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d395b0ba33578892d47863a361d218de574180f1","tid":617481,"uid":31215,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:17:20.000Z","msg":"出呢啲少少事鬼理咩<br />\n香港人：